here is the bug detail

if the error.confs looks like
`"error.confs": [
          {
            "values": [
              "hive_none"
            ], 
            "type": "enumeration", 
            "column.name": "abc"
          }
        ]`

the where clause is `(((`abc` IN ())) OR (`abc` IS NULL))`, it is a wrong where clause. It should be `(`abc` IS NULL)`

The pr fixes this bug.

